#{120}{}{Why should I like them? I17m working my ass off to feed my family. And these marauders just got themselves some bikes and guns to play the tough guys. I would like to see them try to stay here and work on the crops for a few years! Although, of course, this is not my main gripe with them. They can live as they want to, I just want them to stay away from me and away from Bridgeport.}
{120}{}{我为什么要喜欢它们？我拼命工作养家糊口。这些掠夺者给自己弄了一些自行车和枪来对付那些硬汉。我希望他们能在这里工作几年！当然，这不是我对他们的主要抱怨。他们可以随心所欲地生活，我只希望他们远离我，远离布里奇波特。}
