#{131}{}{He just doesn17t understands yet. Having your own home - what can be better? He decided to exchange his family for the highway. Dtupid fool... By the time he understands that this is a waste of his life, it will be too late. He needs to have some sense beaten into him, before that scum take him away from home. Can you help?}
{131}{}{他只是还不明白。有自己的家-还有什么比这更好的呢？他决定用家人换高速公路。傻瓜。。。等他明白这是在浪费他的生命时，就太晚了。在那个人渣把他从家里带走之前，他需要有点理智。你能帮忙吗？}
#{132}{}{I don17t know... How do we do that?}
